des: It’s no mystery. Waking up just got a lot more interesting, Dateline-style. Enable this skill, and Andrea Canning, Keith Morrison and Dennis Murphy will wake you up every day! Just say, "Alexa, set an alarm to Dateline!" Oh, and there’s a twist: Beware the snooze. Josh Mankiewicz can get a little testy. But you already knew that, didn’t you?
